		<h3 class="text-2xl font-semibold text-white group-hover:text-green-300 transition">
			Personal Portfolio Website
		</h3>
		<p class="text-gray-400 mt-2">
			A portfolio site to showcase my work and experience, built with Astro, Tailwind, and deployed on Vercel.
		</p>
		<ul class="flex gap-3 mt-4 text-sm text-gray-500">
			<li>Astro</li>
			<li>Tailwind</li>
			<li>Vercel</li>
		</ul>
		<div class="mt-4 flex gap-4 text-green-400">
			<a href="https://github.com/" class="hover:underline" target="_blank">GitHub ↗</a>
			<a href="https://your-live-site.com" class="hover:underline" target="_blank">Live ↗</a>
